    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This chassis has undergone a comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure torsional rigidity and prevent the common fatigue points associated with this platform. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, delivering power through a M-Variable Lock differential for superior corner-exit traction. The VANOS system has been professionally overhauled with upgraded seals, and the rod bearings have been replaced as a preventative measure. Suspension geometry remains factory-spec with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing the signature communicative steering rack feel. The paintwork exhibits exceptional depth with no signs of clear coat failure or oxidation. A turn-key example for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 43500.0,
